Pore

class conan.build_modules.structures.Pore(parameters: Dict[str, str | int | float], keywords: List[str])

Bases: Structure

Represents a pore structure.

Attributes:

bond_length (float): The bond length of the structure. sheet_size (List[float]): The size of the sheet. pore_center (List[float]): The center of the pore. cnt_radius (List[float]): The radius of the carbon nanotube.
